# Skyhaven Language & Font Conventions

## Game UI: English Only

**All user-facing text in the game must be in English.** This includes:
- Button labels, menu items, section titles
- Tooltips, error messages, hints
- Tile names, resource labels, status text
- Any string visible to the player in the UI

Use English for consistency and broader reach. Code comments and internal variable names may use any language.

## Fonts

- **Koulen** (`Koulen-Regular.ttf`): Used for buttons (duration pills, action items, generic items, settings chips)
- **Jersey10** (`Jersey10-Regular.ttf`): Used for the Toolbox panel and related UI (tile palette, edit block, resource display)
